---
layout: default
---
.hero
  .col-xs-12.xy-center.text-center
    .stroke-text
      %h1
        Mike
        %span{style: 'font-size: 5vw;vertical-align:middle'} &
        Dan
    %h2 Fast Fixes to Full Features
.gradient-bg
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-9.col-md-offset-1.text-center
        %h2
          How Can We Help?
        %h3
          Mike & Dan is a tag-team knockout for your business. From front-end to
          back, we'll make sure your business is running smoothly and connected
          to the modern world. Below are some of the services that we commonly
          provide for businesses, startups, and non-profits.

.dark-bg
  .container{style: 'padding-top:50px;'}
    %hr
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
        %img{src: "/assets/rocketship.png", class: 'img-responsive'}
      .col-md-6.col-xs-12
        %h2
          Website and Mobile Launch
        %h3
          We like to build <u>responsive</u>, <u>fast</u>, and <u>accessible</u>
          websites, that act as an extension of you and your business. And we
          like to turn those websites into mobile apps! That way you can connect
          with your customers anywhere and everywhere.
    %hr
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
        %h2
          Laser-Focused Optimizations
        %h3
          We only start working on a project after we've identified
          <u>exactly</u> where we can provide the most value in a project.
          That way you can focus on growing your business, without the burden of
          bringing on a full-time developer.
      .col-md-3.col-xs-12
        %img{src: "/assets/magnifyglass.png", class: 'img-responsive'}
    %hr
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
        %img{src: "/assets/conveyor.png", class: 'img-responsive', style: 'padding-top: 10px;'}
      .col-md-6.col-xs-12
        %h2
          Automated Business Services
        %h3
          Beyond getting your business online, we aim to get your
          <i>processes</i> online. Using a special mix of the right cloud
          services for each scenario, we'll help you organize and automate the
          basics, freeing you to focus on the customer (or just sit back
          and enjoy cruise control).
    %hr
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
          %h3
            Ready to find out how the 21st century can affect your business?
          %h4
            Contact us today to start a conversation and see where Mike & Dan
            can help.
          %form#contactform.form-horizontal{method: "POST"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Name:
              .col-sm-10
                %input.form-control{name: "name", type: "text"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Email:
              .col-sm-10
                %input.form-control{name: "_replyto", type: "email"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Organization Name or Website:
              .col-sm-10
                %input.form-control{name: "business", type: "email"}
            .form-group
              %label.col-sm-2.control-label Message:
              .col-sm-10
                %textarea.form-control{name: "notes", rows: "3"}
            %input{name: "_gotcha", style: "display:none", type: "text"}/
            .text-center
              %input.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{type: "submit", value: "Start a Convo"}
          :javascript
            var contactform =  document.getElementById('contactform');
            contactform.setAttribute('action', '//formspree.io/' + 'info' + '@' + 'getmikeanddan' + '.' + 'com');
    %hr
